#

Classic New England Clam Chowder

45 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Dairy-Free OptionLow-Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodSeafood

Description

A creamy and hearty soup packed with tender clams and potatoes, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • clams: 2 cans (6.5 oz each)
  • potatoes: 2 medium, diced
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • celery: 1 stalk, chopped
  • bacon: 4 slices, diced
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • milk: 1 cup
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • flour: 2 tablespoons
  • chicken broth: 2 cups
